en_402950_0	Colonel Shantha Hewage of Sri Lanka Artillery assumed duties as the new officiating Brigade Commander of the 661 Infantry Brigade under the 66 Division of the Security Forces - Killinochchi on Monday (18).
en_402950_1	The newly-appointed officiating Brigade Commander was greeted to a Guard Turnout on arrival at entrance of the 661 Infantry Brigade.
en_402950_2	To mark the memorable event, the new Brigade Commander planted a sapling in the Brigade Headquarters and addressed All Rankers before he participated in All Rank tea table.
en_402950_3	Commanding Officers of under command Battalions and Staff Officers serving in the Brigade were present during the ceremony.
